help_quota_mail=You can use the following variables to create the text:

${ZARAFA_QUOTA_NAME} - the name of the zarafa account
${ZARAFA_QUOTA_STORE_SIZE} - the current size of the account
${ZARAFA_QUOTA_WARN_SIZE} - the limit to get a warning
${ZARAFA_QUOTA_SOFT_SIZE} - the limit where sending gets disallowed
${ZARAFA_QUOTA_HARD_SIZE} - the limit where sending and receiving gets disallowed
--
